data.description: JUST REDUCED!!!! MOTIVATED SELLER!!! Beautiful move in ready home in the highly desirable gated community of Eagle Bay Landing. This 4 bedroom 3.5 bath backs up to the state forest where you can watch the deer and other wildlife from your covered patio. This open floor concept is perfect for entertaining. The primary bedroom is located on the 1st floor with a large walk-in closet and bath with a double vanity. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths along with a large family/game room and large laundry room.
